    title: 'Healthcare Facility Renovation Charlotte: Upgrading Aging Medical Buildings',
    slug: 'healthcare-facility-renovation-charlotte',
    excerpt:
      'A practical guide to renovating aging healthcare facilities in Charlotte NC — code compliance upgrades, infection control during construction, phased renovation strategies, and cost considerations.',
    date: '2026-04-02',
